quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  12,43,(Rex dictus ego vide 7 fat cows devoured 7 skinny cows 7 green spikes wheat) others shriveled O my senior advise me regarding my dream vos know quam interpret dreams
  12,44,They dictus Nonsense dreams When it advenit interpretation de dreams nos est knowledgeable
  12,45,(Unus saved prison) dictus nunc he tandem remembered ego tell vos its interpretation ita send me Joseph
  12,46,Joseph my friend inform nos 7 fat cows devoured 7 skinny cows 7 green spikes others shriveled Ego wish to iit some information people
  12,47,He dictus Quod vos cultivate deinde 7 annus when temporis harvest advenit sinister grains their spikes absque pro quod vos eat
  12,48,"Post ut, 7 annus drought advenit qui testimentum consume multus de quod vos stored them"
  12,49,"Post ut, annus advenit brings relief people they dodum again press juice"